flowchart TD
    Start([HTTP 请求]) --> Netty[Netty Server<br/>Reactor Netty]
    Netty --> DH[DispatcherHandler]

    DH --> HM[RouterFunctionMapping<br/>或 RequestMappingHandlerMapping]
    HM --> HF[HandlerFunction<br/>或 HandlerMethod]

    DH --> Invoker[HandlerAdapter<br/>invokeHandler]
    Invoker --> H[调用业务方法<br/>返回 Mono/Flux]

    H --> Result[HandlerResult]
    Result --> R[ResultHandler<br/>ServerResponse]

    R --> Resp[Response]

    subgraph BackPressure["背压（Backpressure）"]
        Note[Mono 是 0/1 个元素<br/>Flux 是 0/N 个元素<br/>Subscriber 主动请求 n 个]
    end

    H -.背压.-> BackPressure

    classDef startNode fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0,stroke-width:2px
    classDef handlerNode fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ef6c00
    classDef reactiveNode fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32,stroke-width:2px
    class Start startNode
    class Netty,DH,HM,Invoker handlerNode
    class H,Result,R,Resp reactiveNode
